{"tid":510283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外籍客拒付車資 港男司機被推跌毆打受傷送院","createTime":"2017-12-26T10:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T11:31:42.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"648de0f7b6ca5628911ea9592f90f1863217a391","tid":510283,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"港島半山興漢道，凌晨1時許，一名66歲姓何的士司機，接載一名外籍男乘客到達目的地時，乘客拒絕付款，的士司機討回75元車資期間，遭外籍乘客毆打及推趺地上，傷人後拔足逃去，警員接報到場調查，的士司機手部受傷，腰及臀痛，事後送院敷治。<br />\n<br />\n涉事外籍男約1.8米高、蓄金髮，案發時身穿淺色恤衫及淺色長褲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171225/large/1514143354_cdfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171225%2Flarge%2F1514143354_cdfa.jpg&h=1f58f5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171225/large/1514143352_5f01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171225%2Flarge%2F1514143352_5f01.jpg&h=7f2d264e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b83c73b05f29c05c11dc146f515c53e902880e87","tid":510283,"uid":41508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acecfd10e033c4a3a2fa4164c9451166bce15941","tid":510283,"uid":46769,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"white trash"},{"pid":"bcfb65bf2a2de3157ea0133bf4330e04026f2e0d","tid":510283,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:04:08.000Z","msg":"賤人真係無分國界<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54b5941ad771257e98ebcd7d1af8ee586b4f37f","tid":510283,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"有無兜路"},{"pid":"bccc31f49fbf83536995d9c57e82c5926569aa0c","tid":510283,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:06:50.000Z","msg